FIG. 2 is a schematic block diagram showing an operation of the resolution conversion in accordance with FIG. 1;


FIG. 3 is a schematic block diagram of an apparatus for converting the resolution of an image to the resolution of a LCD monitor in accordance with the principles of the present invention;


